# App-scoped sharing for every knowledge object in this app (dashboard, data model,
# lookup definition, lookup table). All users can read (view the dashboard); only
# admins can edit. A single global [] stanza avoids per-conf metadata stanzas that
# would otherwise require reload triggers in app.conf.
#
# To let ad hoc searches in OTHER apps use this data model/lookup, add a per-object
# stanza with `export = system` (and the matching reload trigger in app.conf).
[]
access = read : [ * ], write : [ admin, sc_admin ]
